                    <h1>Welcome to The Bishee Barnabee</h1>
                    <h2>About us</h2>
                    <p> The Bishee Barnabee Hotel (BBH) is a newly established independent hotel located on the western periphery of Norwich, 
                        within walking distance of the commercial hub of the city. The hospital and research park are nearby, facilitating all
                        business needs and requirements. Accommodation comes in two basic forms: double or twin, supplemented with either a basic 
                        package or premium facilities. Alongside this we provide a range of services to meet your needs. Come dine with us at the 
                        fashionable Bishee Barnabee restaurant (BBR). Stay fit after a decadent night at our newly developed gym facility. 
                        Nothing is off the table as far as we’re concerned. We provide a dedicated online service to manage your bookings. Stay with us. You can stay as long as you like.
                    </p>

                    <hr>

                    <h3>Room packages </h3> <div> <img align ="right" src="recep.jpg" class="img-responsive"> </div>
